@startuml
participant "Sensor Node" as SN
participant "Network Emulator" as NE
participant "Central Processor" as CP
participant "Operator UI" as UI
actor Operator

SN -> NE: DisturbanceEvent (JSON)
note left: monotonic_ns = 1000\ntimestamp_utc = T1
NE -> NE: Apply Latency (e.g. 20ms)
NE -> CP: Forward DisturbanceEvent
note right: Received at T2
CP -> CP: Rule-based Classification
CP -> CP: Wait for > 1s interval 
CP -> CP: Log CentralAlert -> alerts.jsonl
CP -> CP: Write central_state.json
UI -> CP: Read logs safely
UI -> Operator: Display in Dashboard

@enduml
